+We are continuing the development of our Notion Clone web application built with Next.js (App Router), React, and Prisma. In the previous session, due to API limit exhaustion, several critical code changes regarding the Sidebar and Page-Management system were generated or discussed but NOT fully committed/written to the actual files. 
