+- DO NOT hallucinate or delete pre-existing layout structures, authentication wraps, or global providers.
+- If a code block from the previous session was cut in half, reconstruct it completely using proper TypeScript interfaces and error handling (try-catch blocks for database transactions).
+- Verify all Next.js imports (`next/navigation`, `next/link`) use the modern App Router standards instead of the legacy Pages Router.
