+Note deletion is currently completely broken and saved notes cannot be deleted. This issue is highly likely rooted in the user isolation "key system" we implemented earlier (which ensures notes are saved uniquely per device/user and prevents other users from accessing them). The deletion mechanism is failing to execute, likely due to a mismatch between how the isolation keys are validated and how the delete requests/relations are handled in the API or database layers.
